response.title: The Big 5 Personality test
response.description: These are incredibly helpful for understanding yourself. When you understand your own personality, you can ask for your needs, connect more easily, and optimize your behavior

personality_test_questions.question: I see myself as someone who is original, unique, and comes up with new ideas.
I see myself as someone who is sophisticated in art, music, or literature..
I see myself as someone who has a lot of artistic interests.
I see myself as someone who has an active imagination.
I see myself as someone who values artistic and creative experiences.
I see myself as someone who is inventive.
I see myself as someone who does a thorough job.
I see myself as someone who is extremely careful.
I see myself as someone who is a reliable worker.
I see myself as someone who tends to be organized.
I see myself as someone who tends to be diligent.
I see myself as someone who perseveres until the task is finished.
I see myself as someone who does things efficiently.
I see myself as someone who prefers work that is routine.
I see myself as someone who is cerebral and enjoys thinking deeply.
I see myself as someone who makes plans and follows through with them.
I see myself as someone who is not easily distracted.
I see myself as someone who is outgoing.
I see myself as someone who is full of energy.
I see myself as someone who generates a lot of enthusiasm.
I see myself as someone who tends to be loud.
I see myself as someone who has an assertive personality.
I see myself as someone who can be warm and friendly.
I see myself as someone who likes to reflect and ponder different ideas.

I see myself as someone who has a forgiving nature.

I see myself as someone who likes to cooperate with others.
